# Angular RxJS Rules

- Use `takeUntilDestroyed()` for subscriptions tied to Angular lifecycles.
- Prefer `toSignal()` when exposing Observable state to templates.
- Avoid nested subscriptions.
- Prefer async pipe or Signals in templates.
- Keep Observable pipelines readable.
- Handle errors explicitly.
